cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DB, cs.CL 

The paper focuses on predictive analytics and machine learning techniques for developing a recommendation system. This falls under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of deep neural models also suggests the sub-category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of big data, which could fall under the sub-categories of databases (cs.DB) and computational linguistics (cs.CL) for natural language processing.
